BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)
</IN>
<LP>
   WAXMAN INDUSTRIES Inc. (Bedford Heights, Ohio) said it
plans to buy back as many as 750,000 shares of the 9.9
million shares outstanding. Waxman is a supplier to the
home-repair and remodeling market in the U.S. and Canada.
</LP>
